==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: shuĭ dī shí chuān
===Etymology===
Literally: Dripping water wears through rock
===Proverb===
'''[[水]][[滴]][[石]][[穿]]'''
# Little strokes fell great oaks.
